Heat oven to 425 degrees F. In 12-inch nonstick skillet heat oil over medium-high heat. Add Simply Potatoes(R) and basil. Cover; cook 12 to14 minutes, stirring occasionally, until Simply Potatoes(R) are tender and browned. Place pizza crust on ungreased cookie sheet. Top with cooked Simply Potatoes(R), ham, artichokes, tomatoes and cheese. Bake 10 to 12 minutes or until cheese is melted.